{"tid":1811254,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新加坡迎來首位武漢肺炎3歲中國女童","createTime":"2020-01-04T13:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T18:49:22.000Z","uid":268519,"like":370,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"75ed04d4cde8a0ae1f00e3d2bcb64378bb08992d","tid":1811254,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"新加坡衞生部周六（4日）宣布，該國出現首宗疑似不明肺炎個案。據指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>患者為3歲中國女童</strong></span>，她曾到訪武漢。<br />\n該名女童現時在醫院接受隔離觀察及治療，目前情況穩定。初步結果顯示，該個案對<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呼吸道合胞病毒呈陽性反應</span></strong>。呼吸道合胞病毒是導致兒童肺炎的常見原因。<br />\n該名女童<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未曾到訪過</span></strong>出現不明肺炎個案的武漢市華南海鮮市場。醫護人員仍在研究女童的病情。<br />\n<br />\n東網 唔放link了 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouL9S6U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouL9S6U.png&h=2131bed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/wuhan-pneumonia-first-suspect-case-identified-here\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fhealth%2Fwuhan-pneumonia-first-suspect-case-identified-here&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=330d9f12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/wuhan-pneumonia-first-suspect-case-identified-here</a>"},{"pid":"0af4714d10193759869a299d751d63dffec2b56c","tid":1811254,"uid":173271,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Plague Inc.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5720eac91e235b094c128511c3f71b283c4018cd","tid":1811254,"uid":42820,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"喜迎牙爺大禮"},{"pid":"cc7520b9573ff22897f02526582a7900d58d8764","tid":1811254,"uid":40463,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:58:43.000Z","